### Create 
POST http://localhost:3000/students 
Content-Type: application/json 
  
{ 
  "matricNo": "A21CS9999", 
  "name": "Test Student", 
  "course": "BSc CS", 
  "faculty": "FSKSM", 
  "gpa": 3.50, 
  "email": "test@graduate.utm.my", 
  "year": 1, 
  "active": true 
} 
  
### Update (replace <id> with the id returned above) 
PUT http://localhost:3000/students/6 
Content-Type: application/json 
  
{ 
  "matricNo": "A21CS9999", 
  "name": "Test Student (updated)", 
  "course": "BSc CS", 
  "faculty": "FSKSM", 
  "gpa": 3.80, 
  "email": "test@graduate.utm.my", 
  "year": 2, 
  "active": true 
} 
  
### Delete 
DELETE http://localhost:3000/students/6 
